ak]]|| 6\u20130, 6\u20137<sup>(6\u20138)</sup>, [10\u20132]\n|- \n|[[2009 Copa Telmex|2009]] || {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Marcel Granollers]]<br>{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Alberto Mart\u00edn]] || {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Nicol\u00e1s Almagro]]<br>{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Santiago Ventura Bertomeu|Santiago Ventura]]|| 6\u20133, 5\u20137, [10\u20138]\n|-\n|[[2010 Copa Telmex|2010]] || {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Sebasti\u00e1n Prieto (tennis)|Sebasti\u00e1n Prieto]] <small>(3)</small><br>{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Horacio Zeballos]] || {{flagicon|GER}} [[Simon Greul]]<br>{{flagicon|AUS}} [[Peter Luczak]]|| 7&ndash;6<sup>(7\u20134)</sup>, 6&ndash;3\n|-\n|[[2011 Copa Claro|2011]] || {{flagicon|AUT}} [[Oliver Marach]]<br>{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Leonardo Mayer]] || {{flagicon|BRA}} [[Franco Ferreiro]]<br>{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Andr\u00e9 S\u00e1]]|| 7\u20136<sup>(8\u20136)</sup>, 6\u20133\n|-\n|[[2012 Copa Claro|2012]] || {{flagicon|ESP}} [[David Marrero]]<br>{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Fernando Verdasco]] || {{flagicon|SVK}} [[Michal Merti\u0148\u00e1k]]<br>{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Andr\u00e9 S\u00e1]]|| 6\u20134, 6\u20134\n|-\n|[[2013 Copa Claro|2013]] || {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Simone Bolelli]]<br>{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Fabio Fognini]] || {{flagicon|USA}} [[Nicholas Monroe]]<br>{{flagicon|GER}} [[Simon Stadler]]|| 6\u20133, 6\u20132\n|-\n|[[2014 Copa Claro|2014]] || {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Marcel Granollers]] <small>(2)</small><br>{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Marc L\u00f3pez]] || {{flagicon|URU}} [[Pablo Cuevas]]<br>{{flagicon|ARG}} [[Horacio Zeballos]]|| 7\u20135, 6\u20134\n|-\n|[[2015 Argentina Open|2015]] || {{flagicon|FIN}} [[Jarkko Nieminen]]<br>{{flagicon|BRA}} [[Andr\u00e9 S\u00e1]] || {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Pablo And\u00fajar]]<br>{{flagicon|AUT}} [[Oliver Marach]]||4\u20136, 6\u20134, [10\u20137]\n|-\n|[[2016 Argentina Open|2016]] || {{flagicon|COL}} [[Juan Sebasti\u00e1n Cabal]]<br />{{flagicon|COL}} [[Robert Farah (tennis)|Robert Farah]] || {{flagicon|ESP}} [[I\u00f1igo Cervantes]]<br /> {{flagicon|ITA}} [[Paolo Lorenzi]]|| 6\u20133, 6\u20130\n|-\n|[[