\n|}\n\n{{notelist}}\n\n==Honours==\n=== Club ===\n'''V\u00e9lez Sarsfield'''\n* [[Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n]]: [[2004\u201305 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n#Torneo Clausura|2005 Clausura]]\n* [[Supercopa Argentina]]: [[2013 Supercopa Argentina|2013]]\n\n'''Lazio'''\n* [[Coppa Italia]]: [[2008\u201309 Coppa Italia|2008\u201309]]\n* [[Supercoppa Italiana]]: [[2009 Supercoppa Italiana|2009]]\n\n'''Boca Juniors'''\n*[[Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|Primera Divisi\u00f3n]]: [[2019\u201320 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n|2019\u201320]]\n* [[Supercopa Argentina]]: [[2018 Supercopa Argentina|2018]]\n\n=== National team ===\n'''Argentina U20'''\n* [[FIFA World Youth Championship]]: [[2007 FIFA U-20 World Cup|2007]]\n\n=== Individual ===\n* [[List of Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n top scorers|Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n top scorer]]: [[2006\u201307 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n#Torneo Apertura|2006 Apertura]], [[2013\u201314 Argentine Primera Divisi\u00f3n season#Torneo Final|2014 Final]] (both with V\u00e9lez Sarsfield)\n\n==Notes==\n{{reflist|group=\"nb\"}}\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n==External links==\n{{commons category}}\n* [http://www.velezsarsfield.com.ar/futbol/plantel/perfil/136-mzarate.shtml Profile] at V\u00e9lez Sarsfield's official website\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20110711061529/http://www.futbolxxi.com/Futbolista.aspx?ID=13012&SEOFutbolista=Zarate+Mauro+Matias Argentine Primera statistics] at Futbol XXI {{in lang|es}} \n* {{Soccerbase}}\n\n<!--{{Watford F.C. squad}}-->\n{{Boca Juniors squad}}\n{{Argentina Primera Division top scorers}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Zarate, Mauro}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1987 births]]\n[[Category:People from Mor\u00f3n Partido]]\n[[Category:Argentine footballers]]\n[[Category:Argentina under-20 international footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Club Atl\u00e9tico V\u00e9lez Sarsfield footballers]]\n[[Category:Boca Juniors footballers]]\n[[Category:Al Sadd SC playe