ing]]\n*[[Marlou Slaghuis]]\n'''Head Coach''':\n*[[Robin van Galen]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==={{wpw|RUS}}===\n{{col-begin-small}}\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Olga Fomicheva]]\n*[[Yulia Gaufler]]\n*[[Nadezda Glyzina]]\n*[[Evgeniya Ivanova (Russian water polo)|Evgeniya Ivanova]]\n*[[Sofia Konoukh]]\n*[[Ekaterina Kuzbetsova]]\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Ekaterina Pantyulina]]\n*[[Evgeniya Protsenko]]\n*[[Natalya Ryzhova-Alenicheva]]\n*[[Natalya Shepelina]]\n*[[Elena Smurova]]\n*[[Ekaterina Tankeyeva]]\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Aleksandra Vorobeva]]\n*[[Alena Vylegzhanina]]\n*[[Anastasia Zubkova]]\n'''Head Coach''':\n*[[Alexander Kleymenov]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==={{wpw|SRB}}===\n{{col-begin-small}}\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Dijana Berak]] \n*[[Ivana \u0106orovi\u0107]]\n*[[Eleonora \u0110uri\u0107]] \n*[[Aleksandra Dun\u0111erski]] \n*[[Dragana Ivkovi\u0107]]\n*[[Vladana Joveti\u0107]]\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Nastasja Kne\u017eevi\u0107]] \n*[[Aleksandra Lazarevi\u0107]]\n*[[Izolda Ma\u0161ic]]\n*[[Milica Perovski]]\n*[[Sonja Stankovi\u0107]]\n*[[Natasa Vezili\u0107]]\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Dejana Vukadinov]] \n*[[Jovana Zlokolica]]\n*[[Bojana Zrni\u0107]]\n'''Head Coach''':\n*[[Petar Kova\u010devi\u0107]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==={{wpw|ESP}}===\n{{col-begin-small}}\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Clara Aller]]\n*[[Olga Domenech]]\n*[[Elisabet Gazulla]]\n*[[Blanca Gil]]\n*[[Irene Hagen]]\n*[[Carol Lopez]]\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Cristina L\u00f3pez Aliaga|Cristina L\u00f3pez]]\n*[[Laura Lopez (water polo)|Laura Lopez]]\n*[[Miriam Lopez Escribano]]\n*[[Ona Meseguer]]\n*[[Jennifer Pareja]]\n*[[Anna Pardo]]\n{{col-3}}\n*[[Cristina Pardo Perarnau|Cristina Pardo]]\n*[[Pilar Pe\u00f1a]]\n*[[Patricia del Soto]]\n'''Head Coach''':\n*[[Mar Sanroma]]\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Preliminary round==\n\n===GROUP A===\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align:center\"\n|- bgcolor=\"#DCDCDC\"\n!width=\"25\" |\n!width=\"200\"|Team\n!width=\"60\"|Points\n!width=\"60\"|G\n!width=\"60\"|W\n!width=\"60\"|D\n!width=\"60\"|L\n!width=\"60\"|GF\n!width=\"60\"|GA\n!width=\"60\"|Diff\n|- bgcolor=#AAFFAA\n|1.\n|a